'''Bangladesh''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was added to [[BitLife: Life Simulator|BitLife]] in the May 10, 2020 update, alongside [[Algeria]], [[Bolivia]], [[Croatia]], [[Georgia]], [[Hungary]], [[Jordan]], [[Qatar]], [[Slovakia]], and [[Zimbabwe]]. Its default cities are the capital, Dhaka, along with Chittagong, Gazipur, Khulna, and Narayanganj.

Being an Islam-based country, female characters in BitLife will wear hijabs when they are adults. However unlike [[Afghanistan]], [[Iran]], [[Iraq]], [[Saudi Arabia]], or the [[United Arab Emirates|UAE]] females do not have hijabs in Bangladesh.

